title: Ça ne sortira pas d'ici
overview: Michel Cymes, the most popular doctor in France, assisted by Jennie-Anne Walker as a wacky medical secretary, receives personalities and gives them medical examinations full of mischief, humor, confidences and surprises to learn more about their health and ours.What makes their hearts beat or, on the contrary, their temperature rise? Who or what are they addicted to? What makes them sick in the world today? How do they manage their complexes, disorders, tocs and other phobias? All these questions will be addressed during the consultations of Doctor Cymès in It will not come out of here . Thanks to the expertise and sound advice of Dr. Cymes, you will discover new and surprising anecdotes about the guests but also about your own health.Open-hearted interviews, scalpel portraits and a battery of not always very conventional exams: with this unprecedented medical talk show, we promise you laughter and confidences on prescription!  Michel Cymès, the presenter of the show The extraordinary powers of the human body offers you a new season of his medical consultations, in his office this time, for a complete and staggered check up.  Jennie-Anne Walker is an actress and humorist of Quebec origin trained in the improvisation league.
